cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques to identify individuals based on their body shape and motion dynamics using depth images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses a combination of convolutional and recurrent neural networks, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper formulates the problem as a reinforcement learning task, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of spatio-temporal signatures and attention-based models could also suggest a connection to cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
